data.description: Charm meets functionality in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem. As you walk through the front door, you'll immediately notice the beautiful stained concrete floors that flow seamlessly throughout the residence, setting the tone for a modern yet inviting atmosphere. The master suite doesn't disappoint, offering a dual vanity in the en-suite bathroom, creating a spa-like retreat to start and end your day. Culinary enthusiasts will appreciate the well-appointed kitchen, featuring stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, setting the stage for all your cooking endeavors. Parking will never be an issue with the spacious double garage, making storage and vehicle protection a breeze. Step outside to your expansive yard, perfect for gatherings or furry friends! Schedule your showing today!
